<plot>LOVE-IN is a theatrical celebration of the music of 1967's Summer of Love, featuring legendary artists and a spectacular psychedelic light show. Rock n' roll never felt so good! Tony Award-winning Broadway star, Ben Vereen, sings, dances and hosts the show. Artists include Grammy Award-winning guitarist, Eric Johnson, '60's British Invasion greats, Peter &amp; Gordon, founder of the Youngbloods, Jesse Colin Young, singer/drummer for Electric Flag and Jimi Hendrix, Buddy Miles, lead guitarist from Vanilla Fudge, Vince Martell, the legendary psychedelic band, Strawberry Alarm Clock, soul and blues singer, Earl Thomas and sitar virtuoso Kartik Seshadri, the foremost disciple of Ravi Shankar, accompanied by tabla master, Arup Chattopadhyay.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?345771</url></doc>
